<center>
<h3>MULTIPLE FACULTY POSITIONS</h3>
</center>
<p class="HTMLBody">The <strong>Bourns College of Engineering</strong> invites applications for the following tenure-track and tenured faculty positions in Engineering as well as cross disciplinary hires with potential home departments in Engineering and/or other units within UCR.</p>
<p class="HTMLBody"><span style="font-size: medium; color: #ff9900;"><strong>Faculty positions in Engineering:</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Full Professor position in Bioengineering/Biomedical Engineering and Bioengineering Department Chair</strong>
<ul>
<li><span style="color: #333399;"><em><a href="https://aprecruit.ucr.edu/apply/JPF00243"><span style="color: #333399;">Apply Here&gt;</span></a></em></span></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li class="HTMLBody"><span style="color: #000000;"><strong>Tenure track and tenured positions in Computer Science and Engineering Department in (1) Computer Graphics, Animation, and Gaming 2) Software Engineering.</strong></span>
