<h5>Interdisciplinary Program Link</h5>
<p><a href="http://cmsmse.engr.ucr.edu/">Material Science and Engineering<br /></a><a href="http://cen.ucr.edu/">Computer Engineering</a></p>
<h5>Interdisciplinary Centers:</h5>
<p><a href="http://www.bioeng.ucr.edu/">Center for Bioengineering Research</a>&nbsp;(CBR)<br /><a href="http://www.cert.ucr.edu/">Center for Environmental Research and Technology (CE-CERT)</a><br /><a href="http://www.cnse.ucr.edu/">Center for Nanoscale Science and Engineering (CNSE)<br /></a>Center for Phonon Optimized Engineered Materials (POEM)<br /><a style="font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.5em;" href="http://www.cris.ucr.edu/index.php">Center for Research in Intelligent Systems (CRIS)<br /></a><a href="http://www.uclight.ucr.edu/"><span style="font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.5em;">Center for Ubiquitous Communication by Light (UC-LIGHT)</span><br /></a><a href="http://www.scrise.ucr.edu/"><span style="font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.5em;">S</span>outhern California Research Initiative for Solar Energy(SC-RISE)</a><br /><a href="http://www.wcgec.ucr.edu/">Winston Chung Global Energy Center&nbsp;(WCGEC)</a></p>
